PortSystem 1.0

name			nauty
version         2.6r10
categories		math science
license         Apache-2
platforms       darwin
maintainers		nomaintainer
homepage		http://pallini.di.uniroma1.it/
master_sites	${homepage}
distname		${name}[strsed ${version} {g/\.//}]
worksrcdir      ${distname}

description		nauty is a program for computing automorphism groups of \
				graph and digraphs.
long_description \
				nauty and Traces are programs for computing automorphism \
                groups of graphs and digraphs. They can also produce a \
                canonical label. There is a small suite of programs called \
                gtools included in the package. For example, geng can generate \
                non-isomorphic graphs very quickly. There are also generators \
                for bipartite graphs, digraphs, and multigraphs, and \
                programs for manipulating files of graphs in a compact format.

checksums       rmd160  d1c82ee5078afbd6b45286a139405f771e457208 \
                sha256  065f8d08f2c3f301f47b472a26ec8e2d7d8750d671722248afe61b03209ded9a

